data.description: Don't pass up this 5 bed 2 bath home in the heart of Bethalto. House needs a little updating, but with a little work this home could be your dream home. Great location, full partially finished basement that offers plenty of room for a den, workshop and more. Large room off the back of kitchen would possibly make a great family room. Oversized two plus car garage/workshop is heated and offers plenty of space. Large driveway area in front of garage offers plenty of additional parking. Priced to sell. Home is being offered in a as is condition, seller will not pay for any repairs/upgrades as a result of inspections.
